story.text: At my place of the [[Smallest Federated Wiki]] I am [[Silke Helfrich]] and I'm working on the commons and care for Mapping as a commons as opposed to Mapping the Commons, whereas I also love the latter. But most importantly, I am co-constructing here what I call [[Patterns of Commoning]].
